io.konik.zugferd.entity

Class TaxRegistration

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.konik.zugferd.entity.TaxRegistration

  • public class TaxRegistration
extends Object
    The Class TaxRegistration represents the tax number and its type.
    The ID.getValue() is value added tax identification number
    The ID.getSchemeId() is the Tax payer's number or VAT number according to (UNCL 1153) eg. FC or VA
